          "description": "Pediatric Emergency Room Staff Was Great. Arrived after calling multiple Urgent Care Centers, which were all jammed with one-hour+ waits. My 2 year old grandson hurt his arm playing and was very upset and untouchable there. The staff were all very kind and caring. One x-ray later we learned nothing serious happened. Success! The place was spotless too.",
